    {
      "title": "Alert Rules Reference",
      "description": "Summary of all 6 alert rules for the Risk Mitigation Advisor agent with conditions, severity, and notification channels.",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "h": 10, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 105 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## EUDR-025 Risk Mitigation Advisor Alert Rules\n\n| # | Alert | Condition | Severity | Evaluation | Action |\n|---|-------|-----------|----------|------------|--------|\n| 1 | **Plan Overdue** | Active plans with status = 'delayed' and target_end_date < NOW() > 3 for 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 15m | Review delayed plans, escalate to compliance lead |\n| 2 | **Budget Exceeded** | budget_spent > budget_allocated on any active plan | Critical | Every 5m, for 5m | Freeze additional spend, review allocation |\n| 3 | **Low Effectiveness** | composite_reduction_pct < 10% after 90 days of active mitigation | Warning | Every 1h, for 24h | Review strategy, consider replacement |\n| 4 | **High Drift** | Unresolved critical/high trigger events > 0 for 4 hours | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, activate emergency response |\n| 5 | **ML Degradation** | ml_fallback_total > 50% of recommendations in 1h | Warning | Every 5m, for 15m | Investigate model health, check data pipeline |\n| 6 | **System Errors** | API error rate (5xx) > 1% for 5 minutes | Critical | Every 1m, for 5m | Page on-call, check infrastructure |\n\n### Notification Channels\n- **Critical**: PagerDuty + Slack #eudr-critical + Email compliance-lead\n- **Warning**: Slack #eudr-alerts + Email on-call\n\n### Runbook Links\n- [Strategy Recommendation Troubleshooting](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/strategy-recommendation)\n- [Remediation Plan Overdue Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/plan-overdue)\n- [Budget Exceeded Response](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/budget-exceeded)\n- [Low Effectiveness Investigation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/low-effectiveness)\n- [Trigger Event Escalation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/trigger-escalation)\n- [ML Model Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/ml-degradation)\n- [Optimization Timeout](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/optimization-timeout)\n- [Performance Degradation](https://runbooks.greenlang.io/eudr/rma/perf-degradation)"
      }
    }
